data.description: 4 bedroom 3 bath ranch style home on 4 acres in secluded gated subdivision with plenty of room to play and entertain.  Oversized garage  with work area.  Laundry room with counter space and pantry with room for additional freezer.  Large kitchen with custom cherry wood cabinets with granite, double convection oven, huge freezer and refrigerator, and five burner cooktop.  Huge master suite with large 10 x 20 walk-in closet, double sink, large shower with two shower heads, and whirlpool tub.  Covered back deck with custom iron railing. Call for more information or to set up a viewing 501-912-0107.
data.whatILove: The kitchen is the focal point of the house with tons of counter space and the ability to have large gatherings.  The security of the gated entrance and lack of drive by traffic is ideal for kids to play outside.  We added extra insulation in the house with the complete remodel in 2008 and the energy bills are extremely low for a house this size. If you are looking for a peaceful residence with easy access to work and the city then this is the house for you.
